videos.description: Providence's Rodney Bullock gets the lob from Kyron Cartwright and finishes with the jam.
videos.headline: Friars connect on electric alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Villanova guard Jalen Brunson puts the defender on skates with spin move and layup.
videos.headline: Brunson shows off spin move on layup

videos.description: Villanova's Omari Spellman pump fakes and throws down the vicious jam.
videos.headline: Nova's Spellman punishes rim with thunderous slam

videos.description: Villanova's Omari Spellman gets the feed and gets the hoop and harm.
videos.headline: Nova's Spellman powers through contact for and-1 layup

videos.description: Villanova guard Collin Gillespie uses his pivot to create space and create and and-1 opportunity.
videos.headline: Nova's Gillespie uses footwork to get and-1 layup

videos.description: Providence guard Rodney Bullock gets the dish and converts the huge jam.
videos.headline: Friars' Bullock finishes with emphatic dunk

videos.description: Providence's Isaiah Jackson strips Jalen Brunson and finishes the layup through the contact.
videos.headline: Friars pick Brunson's pocket, finish with and-1 layup

videos.description: Providence guard Rodney Bullock pump fakes and finishes with a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Friars' Bullock skies, finishes with one-handed slam

videos.description: Villanova big man Omari Spellman throws down the one-handed jam that pops out of the basket and drops back in for the hoop and harm.
videos.headline: Nova's Spellman gets lucky bounce on dunk

videos.description: Villanova's Mikal Bridges turns the ball over trying to pass to a player waiting to sub in to the game.
